      <title>巴克莱采取行动削减“数百名”表现不佳的投资银行员工</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/barclays-moves-cut-a-few-hundred-investment-bank-underperformers-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[直接了解此事的消息人士告诉路透社，巴克莱银行已开始新一轮裁员，在其投资银行削减了“数百个职位”，以加大力度解决表现不佳的员工问题并重​​新投资于新人才。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/barclays-moves-cut-a-few-hundred-investment-bank-underperformers-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:58:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
