      <title>美国伦敦房地产支出反弹至八年来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-spending-london-real-estate-rebounds-highest-eight-years-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国巴黎银行房地产部门编制的数据显示，美国投资者正以八年来最快的速度购买伦敦商业地产，原因是有迹象显示英国市场的复苏速度快于遭受重创的美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-spending-london-real-estate-rebounds-highest-eight-years-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 05:02:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚银行因成本上升和抵押贷款竞争而面临利润挤压</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/australia-banks-face-profit-squeeze-rising-costs-mortgage-competition-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚最大的银行可能会报告上半年利润疲弱，因为高运营成本以及销售抵押贷款和存款的竞争挤压了利润率，分析师称股市上涨导致该行业过热，这可能会出现逆转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/australia-banks-face-profit-squeeze-rising-costs-mortgage-competition-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 00:46:58 GMT</pubDate>
